                <p class="text-justify">According to <a href="https://www.faresmatch.com/bangkok-airlines-refund-policy.aspx">Bangkok Airlines Refund Policy</a>, only the unused part of the purchased ticket is subject to a refund. A passenger will be given a refund only if they provide valid payment proof. </p>

