                <h3 class="text-justify">Can a passenger cancel their flight within 24 hours? </h3>

                <p class="text-justify">Yes, a passenger has a choice to cancel their ticket within 24 hours. If the ticket cancellation is within 24 hours, no cancellation fee is charged regardless of the selected fare. </p>

                <h3 class="text-justify">What happens if a passenger cancels their flight on Bangkok Airlines? </h3>

                <p class="text-justify">If a passenger has purchased a basic economy Bangkok airway ticket, they are not entitled to cancel the ticket to get a refund after 24 hours. </p>

                <p class="text-justify">In the case of non-refundable tickets, a minimum fare difference must be paid, which gets credited into the passenger's account in cash or a future travel voucher with which they can purchase a ticket. </p>

                <p class="text-justify">In the case of refundable tickets, a passenger can cancel their ticket any time before the flight, and it will be refunded on the original payment method. </p>

                <h3 class="text-justify">How can a passenger cancel their tickets? </h3>

                <p class="text-justify">Passengers can cancel their tickets online using their mobiles by visiting the Bangkok Airlines website. They can also cancel their tickets by calling the Bangkok Airline reservation department. A passenger can cancel their ticket at the airport by going to the Bangkok Airlines ATO. </p>

